frames.caption: A friendly panda wearing a barista apron stands behind a wooden counter in a cozy coffee shop. The panda is smiling warmly, with a steaming cup of coffee placed in front of it. The background features shelves lined with coffee jars, enhancing the inviting atmosphere.
